  == Introduction
  <introduction>
  This project uses the #stron
g[Video Game Sales with Ratings] dataset
  from Kaggle, which combin
es video game release information, sales data,
  and review scores. Each row represents a v
ideo game, with variables such
  as genre, platform, publisher, year of release, critic s
core, user
  score, and global sales. The goal of this analysis is to predict a
  game's 
global sales using non-sales features such as release year,
  review scores, genre, platf
orm, and publisher group.
  
